text.section:
Before a vehicle is removed from a parking lot, a tower who possesses the vehicle shall release the vehicle to the owner or an agent of the owner:
If the owner or agent requests that the tower release the vehicle;
If the vehicle can be driven under its own power;
Whether or not the vehicle has been lifted off the ground; and
If the owner or agent pays a drop fee to the tower in an amount not exceeding 50% of the cost of a full tow.
